# +-----------+  
# | FvwmPager |  
# +-----------+ 

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmPager: *
*fvwmPager: font none
*fvwmPager: Noseparators
*FvwmPager: Colorset * 3 
*fvwmPager: WindowColorsets 4 5
*FvwmPager: SmallFont 5x8
*FvwmPager: Balloons All
*FvwmPager: BalloonFont "xft:Heiti SC"
*FvwmPager: BalloonYOffset +2
*FvwmPager: BalloonBorderWidth 1
*FvwmPager: UseSkipList
*FvwmPager: MoveThreshold 3
*FvwmPager: SolidSeparators
*FvwmPager: WindowLabelFormat ""
*FvwmPager: WindowBorderWidth 1
*FvwmPager:Geometry 256x36-0-0
Style FvwmPager HandleWidth 0, StaysOnBottom, Sticky, !Title
